Henry Schein | Wolfville, Nova Scotia, Canada (ONSITE) | Full Stack Web Developer | $70k-$90k (CAD) plus benefits

Henry Schein's Global Innovation Center is seeking an experienced Full Stack Web Application Software Engineer with an affinity for working with the latest JavaScript, HTML5, and server side technologies. Located in Wolfville, Nova Scotia, you will join a team with 20+ years experience developing best of breed desktop and web based solutions for Dentistry. Details http://labnet.bitbucket.org/jobs/fullstack.html
